  "content": "<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> At the end of each boss fight, students can contribute to a class legend.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> After a major challenge, students may contribute an assignment to the “Legendary Archive.”</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Creative assignments based on boss battles may become class canon.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Future students may have the opportunity to “battle” past student legends.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Example: Week 10 – Existentialism &amp The Absurd</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Challenge Result</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Legendary Archive Entry</div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>A student defeats Camus’ Stranger in an argument on free will.</div>",
